Module-CAPIMaker
================

This module will allow you to easily provide an efficeint C API for
your XS modules.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Text::Template

